<a href="https://kristaps.bsd.lv/kcgi/khttp_parse.3.html">khttp_parse</a>, <a href="https://kristaps.bsd.lv/kcgi/khttp_parse.3.html">khttp_parsex</a>(3) - parse a CGI instance for kcgi</pre>
			</article>
